{"tid":1996755,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【歷史台】台灣《故事》雜誌登左兩篇我講關於《荷馬史詩》考古發現的文章","createTime":"2020-05-01T07:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T12:51:56.000Z","uid":120678,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"486c5c075c77be6b31498ed8d6f374de41bd21be","tid":1996755,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:15:00.000Z","msg":"傳送門：<br />\n《【荷馬秘事二】考古學家施里曼發現了什麼？》<br />\n<a href=\"https://storystudio.tw/article/gushi/homeric-epic-02/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorystudio.tw%2Farticle%2Fgushi%2Fhomeric-epic-02%2F&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rAZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=c17b7f6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://storystudio.tw/article/gushi/homeric-epic-02/</a><br />\n《【荷馬秘事三】來自西臺泥板的提示》<br />\n<a href=\"https://storystudio.tw/article/gushi/homeric-epic-03/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorystudio.tw%2Farticle%2Fgushi%2Fhomeric-epic-03%2F&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rAZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=454a669c\" target=\"_blank\">https://storystudio.tw/article/gushi/homeric-epic-03/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://storystudio.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/waatar-ma-ekuteni-01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorystudio.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fwaatar-ma-ekuteni-01.jpg&h=916ae63d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文章節錄：<br />\n<br />\n在追尋《荷馬史詩》背後真相時，考古發掘提供的線索和方向往往有其關鍵作用。要確定《荷馬史詩》裡所述的內容有任何歷史根據，第一步就是要確定兩座古城：特洛伊和邁錫尼的存在及所在位置。<br />\n<br />\n提到尋找特洛伊和邁錫尼遺址，不得不提一位在這方面影響深遠的重要人物：德國富商兼業餘考古學者施里曼（Heinrich Schliemann）。話說施里曼是個怎樣的人？<br />\n<br />\n首先，他是一個成功商人，同時亦是考古史上一奇男子。施里曼深信《荷馬史詩》的真實性，準備投入後半生的時間、精力和積蓄證明自己是正確的。十九世紀的歐美上流社會，很流行出資贊助考古發掘，甚至蔚為風尚。考古一方面作為個人榮譽地位及文化修養的象徵向外界展示，另一方面也有可能為出資者帶來難以估計的寶藏。從國家層面來說，當時歐洲列強爭相充實自己國內的博物館，競爭收藏作品以展示國力。也就在這個背景之下，施里曼開始以充裕的身家作後盾，依循畢生的願望尋訪特洛伊的所在。<br />\n<br />\n機緣巧合之下，施里曼在 1868 年遇上英國考古學家卡爾沃特（Frank Calvert）， 卡爾沃特相信特洛伊真正所在地位於希沙利克（Hisarlık），並曾經於 1865 年進行過考古試挖。施里曼起初抱持著懷疑態度，但後來被卡爾沃特說服，開始投資上址的考古工作。有些事情真正嘗試之前不知道，但一挖結果就不得了。<br />\n<br />\n施里曼發現，希沙利克的土丘由近至古總共 9 層，標誌著此地曾經多次毀滅，又多次被重建，因此很大機會是一個重要的聚居地，暗示此城正是特洛伊的機會亦大大提高。施里曼的投資和多年的夢想，終於都開始得到回報。"},{"pid":"6bba5a748386189420c2346cfd6e2fe0664c6ef3","tid":1996755,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5319dbca4954ca7bbe2927c2f6a005ea001a01f3","tid":1996755,"uid":42364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:38:19.000Z","msg":"巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a35ed731158c1fc2ac74e4037b842e427f874e","tid":1996755,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關於西臺我淨係睇過你寫既文"},{"pid":"ce41b3416a40e32373e78ecca8bd5203d2510178","tid":1996755,"uid":120678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8a35ed731158c1fc2ac74e4037b842e427f874e","tid":1996755,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關於西臺我淨係睇過你寫既文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:45:02.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實而家都有keep住出新post，最近講緊魁北克獨立運動既歷史源起，逢星期四出文<br />\n因為同本雜誌簽左合約唔可以響連登或任何地方轉載內文，所以冇響度出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有興趣可以上《Fortune Insight》度睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/483382\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprime.fortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F483382&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rAZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=292ee281\" target=\"_blank\">https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/483382</a>"},{"pid":"5cea00ea2c26f84fe8f683b082c5e84e62963a00","tid":1996755,"uid